code: import axios from"axios";var baseUrl="api/notes/";export var getAll=function getAll(){try{return axios.get(baseUrl).then(function(res){return res.data;});}catch(error){console.log(error);}};export var create=function create(newObject){try{return axios.post(baseUrl,newObject).then(function(res){return res.data;});}catch(error){console.log(error);}};export var update=function update(id,newObject){try{return axios.put("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id),newObject).then(function(res){return res.data;});}catch(error){console.log(error);}};export var remove=function remove(id){try{return axios.delete("".concat(baseUrl,"/").concat(id)).then(function(res){return res.data;});}catch(error){console.log(error);}};
